Class DataStreamFilter

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.sensorhub.api.resource.ResourceFilter<IDataStreamInfo>
      • org.sensorhub.api.datastore.obs.DataStreamFilter
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.util.function.Predicate<IDataStreamInfo>, IQueryFilter
    public class DataStreamFilter
extends ResourceFilter<IDataStreamInfo>

    Immutable filter object for system data streams.
    There is an implicit AND between all filter parameters.
    If internal IDs are used, no other filter options are allowed.
